    "title": "Flee the Wave, Dude!",
    "description": "Fires 13 slow, horizontal projectiles that travel in a wave-like path. Shots pierce targets and can ricochet up to 3 times off surfaces. Jakobs shotgun: +30 percent critical hit damage. Red text: Flee the Wave, Dude!"
  },
  "notes": "Originally featured as a Loot Hunt drop from DJ Tanner; a hotfix later boosted its damage and increased the ricochet behaviour. In cramped spaces the bouncing pellets can easily down the user. Maya can exploit the multi-hit pattern for strong Life Tap healing and quick reload pacing. Gaige with Close Enough benefits heavily, as missed shots and bounces can still redirect into enemies and potentially strike repeatedly in enclosed rooms.",
